
Step 1: Install Java version 1.2 or better on your computer (from http://java.sun.com/j2se/1.4/download.html, select the JRE dowload for your computer)

Step 2: Set the JAVA_HOME environment variable to your java installation directory

Step 3: Unzip cvsgrab_v1.0.zip or cvsgrab_v1.0.tar

To run cvsgrab, from the command line do:
cd <cvsgrab install dir>
cvsgrab <options>

